=============================================== ForestSetting =============================================
-------------------------------------------- (src/setting.h) ----------------------------------------------
domain          |   * the number of variables
                |   * variable order (not implemented)
encodingType    |   {TERMINAL, EDGE_PLUS, EDGE_PLUSMOD, EDGE_MULT}
mergeType       |   {PUSH_UP, PUSH_DOWN, SHORTEN_I, SHORTEN_X} see comments in "setting.h"
name            |   predefined BDD/MXD type, or user defined name
---------------------------------------- (src/settings/range.h) -------------------------------------------
range           |   * range type: {Boolean, Finite, non-neg Finite, Integer, non-neg Real, Real}
                |   * value type: {void, int, long, float, double}
                |   * max range N for range type "Finite"
                |   * flags of allowing special values: negative infinity, postive infinity, or undefined
------------------------------------- (src/settings/reductions.h) -----------------------------------------
reductions      |   * dimension: 1 or 2
                |   * predefined type including "user_defined"
                |   * vector of bool encoding set of reduction rules allowed
------------------------------------- (src/settings/edge_flags.h) -----------------------------------------
flags           |   * swap flag type
                |   * complement flag type
